# GHXSTSHIP Industries Website - Full Stack Development Brief

## üéØ Project Overview

Create a full-stack immersive entertainment, experiential marketing, and creative media production agency website for **GHXSTSHIP Industries LLC** (dba GHXSTSHIP). 

**Design Aesthetic:** Contemporary Minimal Pop Art in pure black, white, and greyscale with bold geometric compositions and brutalist typography.

**Inspiration Sources:**
- Acceleration Community of Companies (https://www.accelerationcc.com/) - Full-screen immersive sections, smooth animations
- Pink Sparrow (https://www.pinksparrow.com/) - Bold, graphic-forward design, high-energy aesthetic

---

## üè¢ Company Information

**Legal Name:** GHXSTSHIP Industries LLC  
**DBA:** GHXSTSHIP  
**Headquarters:** Tampa, FL  
**Team Structure:** Global Remote  
**Founded:** December 2022 (Legally organized July 2023)

### Core Verticals
1. Immersive Entertainment
2. Experiential Marketing
3. Creative Media
4. Integrated Technology

### Service Framework (The 4 D's)
1. **DESIGN** - Conceptual development & creative strategy
2. **DEVELOPMENT (PRODUCTION)** - Build, fabricate, produce
3. **DIRECTION (OPERATIONS)** - Execute, manage, deliver
4. **DISRUPTION (INNOVATION)** - Push boundaries, create the future

### Avenues of Delivery
- Digital
- Virtual
- Physical
- Experiential
- Theatrical

### Products/Platforms
- **ATLVS** - Experiential Project Management Platform (https://atlvs.one)
- **GVTEWAY** - Experiential Community Management & Access (Ticketing) - Coming Soon

