## üé® Design System

### Color Palette - MONOCHROMATIC ONLY
```javascript
// Tailwind Config - colors
colors: {
  black: '#000000',      // Primary backgrounds, bold text, graphic elements
  white: '#FFFFFF',      // Primary backgrounds, contrast text, highlights
  grey: {
    100: '#F5F5F5',      // Lightest grey, subtle backgrounds
    200: '#E5E5E5',      // Light grey, borders, dividers
    300: '#D4D4D4',      // Mid-light grey
    400: '#A3A3A3',      // Medium grey, secondary text
    500: '#737373',      // Mid grey
    600: '#525252',      // Mid-dark grey
    700: '#404040',      // Dark grey
    800: '#262626',      // Darker grey
    900: '#171717',      // Almost black, deep backgrounds
  }
}
```

**Usage Rules:**
- ‚úÖ Backgrounds: Alternate between pure black and pure white for maximum contrast
- ‚úÖ Text: Black on white, white on black only
- ‚úÖ Accents: Use grey tones for borders, dividers, subtle backgrounds
- ‚úÖ Hover States: Invert colors (black ‚Üî white)
- ‚úÖ Images: Convert ALL images to duotone/high-contrast B&W
- ‚úÖ Geometric Shapes: Pure black or white with optional grey fills
- ‚ùå NO COLOR: Absolutely no color except black, white, and greyscale

### Typography System
```javascript
// Tailwind Config - fontFamily
fontFamily: {
  'anton': ['Anton', 'Impact', 'Arial Black', 'sans-serif'],
  'bebas': ['Bebas Neue', 'Arial Narrow', 'Arial', 'sans-serif'],
  'share': ['Share Tech', 'Monaco', 'Consolas', 'monospace'],
  'share-mono': ['Share Tech Mono', 'Courier New', 'Courier', 'monospace'],
}
```

#### ANTON - Title & H1
**Usage:** Main site title, hero headlines, major impact statements  
**Weight:** Regular (400) - single weight font  
**Transform:** UPPERCASE preferred  
**Sizes:**
- Desktop: 72px - 120px+ (heroes)
- Mobile: 48px - 72px
**Line Height:** 0.9 - 1.1 (tight for impact)  
**Letter Spacing:** -0.02em to 0  
**Colors:** Pure black or pure white only  
**Examples:** "GHXSTSHIP", "WE CREATE WORLDS"
```css
/* Example CSS */
.title-hero {
  font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(48px, 10vw, 120px);
  line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
```

#### BEBAS NEUE - H2 through H6
**Usage:** Section headers, subsections, category labels, navigation  
**Weight:** Regular (400) or Bold (700)  
**Transform:** UPPERCASE for H2-H3, flexible for H4-H6  
**Sizes:**
- H2: 40px - 56px (desktop) / 28px - 36px (mobile)
- H3: 32px - 40px (desktop) / 24px - 28px (mobile)
- H4: 24px - 32px (desktop) / 20px - 24px (mobile)
- H5: 20px - 24px (desktop) / 18px - 20px (mobile)
- H6: 18px - 20px (desktop) / 16px - 18px (mobile)

**Line Height:** 1.1 - 1.2  
**Letter Spacing:** 0.02em - 0.04em  
**Examples:** "DESIGN", "DEVELOPMENT", "SERVICES"
```css
/* Example CSS */
.heading-section {
  font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 56px);
  line-height: 1.15;
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
```

#### SHARE TECH - Body Copy
**Usage:** All body copy, paragraphs, descriptions, general content  
**Weight:** Regular (400) - single weight font  
**Transform:** Normal (sentence case)  
**Sizes:**
- Desktop: 16px - 18px base
- Mobile: 15px - 16px base
- Large body: 18px - 20px

**Line Height:** 1.6 - 1.8 (comfortable reading)  
**Letter Spacing:** 0 to 0.01em  
**Max Width:** 65-75 characters per line  
**Examples:** All descriptive paragraphs, service descriptions
```css
/* Example CSS */
.body-text {
  font-family: 'Share Tech', monospace;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 70ch;
}
```

#### SHARE TECH MONO - Metadata & Subtitles
**Usage:** Metadata, dates, tags, labels, technical info, captions  
**Weight:** Regular (400) - single weight font  
**Transform:** UPPERCASE for labels/tags, normal for captions  
**Sizes:**
- Desktop: 12px - 14px
- Mobile: 11px - 13px
- Large labels: 14px - 16px

**Line Height:** 1.4 - 1.6  
**Letter Spacing:** 0.05em - 0.1em  
**Colors:** Grey 500-600 for metadata, black/white for prominent labels  
**Examples:** "CLIENT: FORMULA 1", "2024", "TAMPA, FL"
```css
/* Example CSS */
.metadata-label {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 13px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #525252; /* grey-600 */
}
```

#### Typography Hierarchy Example
```
ANTON (120px, black, uppercase): GHXSTSHIP
    ‚Üì
ANTON (72px, black, uppercase): WE CREATE BEYOND REALITY
    ‚Üì
BEBAS NEUE (40px, black, uppercase): IMMERSIVE ENTERTAINMENT
    ‚Üì
SHARE TECH (18px, black): We architect impossible experiences that push 
the boundaries of what audiences expect, transforming abstract concepts 
into tangible realities.
    ‚Üì
SHARE TECH MONO (13px, grey-600, uppercase): 
TAMPA, FL  //  EST. 2022  //  52+ COUNTRIES
```

