## üèóÔ∏è Tech Stack

### Frontend
- **Framework:** Next.js 14+ (App Router)
- **Language:** TypeScript
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS with custom design system
- **Animations:** Framer Motion + GSAP for complex sequences
- **3D (Optional):** Three.js or React Three Fiber

### Backend
- **API:** Next.js API Routes or separate Node.js/Express
- **CMS (Optional):** Sanity, Contentful, or Payload CMS

### Tools & Libraries
- **Forms:** React Hook Form with validation
- **Image Processing:** Sharp for duotone/B&W conversion
- **Analytics:** Plausible or Google Analytics

### Hosting & Deployment
- **Platform:** Vercel (preferred)
- **Performance Targets:** Lighthouse 90+ across all metrics
- **Approach:** SSR/SSG where appropriate for SEO

