## üìê Site Structure

### Primary Pages

#### 1. HOMEPAGE

**Hero Section**
- Full-screen bold graphic composition
- Large ANTON typography: "GHXSTSHIP"
- Abstract geometric ghost ship silhouette (black/white/grey layers)
- Tagline (Bebas Neue): "WE CREATE BEYOND REALITY"
- High contrast black background with white elements
- Minimal geometric scroll indicator

**Who We Are**
- 2-3 sentence intro (Share Tech)
- Statistics counter (Bebas Neue): "52+ COUNTRIES", "13+ YEARS", "XX PROJECTS"
- Animated halftone globe or geometric network
- Bold horizontal rules as dividers

**The 4 D's (Services)**
- Four full-screen sections (one per D)
- Bebas Neue headings with geometric icons
- Share Tech descriptions
- Alternating black/white backgrounds
- Bold geometric shapes as backgrounds
- Hover: scale and contrast shifts

**Verticals Grid**
- Strong geometric framing
- Bold black or white cards
- Duotone imagery per vertical
- Bebas Neue labels
- Click to filter projects

**Featured Projects**
- 3-4 hero projects, asymmetric grid
- Large duotone imagery with halftone overlays
- Share Tech Mono metadata
- Quick facts (Bebas Neue): CLIENT, VERTICAL, YEAR, SCOPE
- CTA to full case study

**Products/Platforms**
- Bold graphic blocks for ATLVS and GVTEWAY
- B&W product screenshots
- Share Tech descriptions
- "COMING SOON" badge (Bebas Neue + geometric)

**Call to Action**
- Massive ANTON: "READY TO DISRUPT?"
- Contact form or calendar booking
- Minimal geometric button design
- Office locations (Share Tech Mono)

#### 2. ABOUT / STORY

- ANTON main heading: "THE STORY"
- Bebas Neue section headers
- Share Tech body copy
- Geometric timeline with nodes
- Mission/vision/values in bold graphic cards
- Team approach explanation
- Halftone imagery for timeline events
- Partner logos (B&W lockups): Formula 1, Insomniac, PATR√ìN, Heineken, Red Bull

#### 3. SERVICES

Individual pages/sections for each of the 4 D's:

**DESIGN**
- Creative concepting, brand experiences, spatial design, content strategy

**DEVELOPMENT (PRODUCTION)**
- Production management, fabrication, build-out, technical integration

**DIRECTION (OPERATIONS)**
- Operations management, logistics, on-site execution, talent management

**DISRUPTION (INNOVATION)**
- Innovation lab, emerging tech, R&D, future-forward concepts

**Each Service Includes:**
- ANTON heading for service name
- Bebas Neue subsections
- Share Tech detailed descriptions
- Share Tech Mono capability lists
- Geometric icon system
- Process visualization (bold arrows and shapes)
- Example projects (duotone)
- Related case studies

#### 4. WORK / PROJECTS

**Grid View**
- Filterable by: VERTICAL, SERVICE, YEAR, CLIENT (Bebas Neue labels)
- Duotone thumbnails + Bebas Neue titles + Share Tech Mono tags
- Hover: scale, invert colors
- Click through to case study

**Case Study Template**
- Hero: Duotone/B&W image or video
- ANTON project title
- Bebas Neue section headers: CHALLENGE, SOLUTION, RESULTS
- Share Tech body copy
- Share Tech Mono metadata and captions
- Key metrics in bold geometric callout boxes
- Image gallery (all duotone/B&W)
- Video embeds with custom B&W controls
- Team credits (Share Tech Mono)
- Related projects grid

#### 5. VERTICALS

Individual landing pages:
- **IMMERSIVE ENTERTAINMENT:** Concerts, festivals, tours, theatrical
- **EXPERIENTIAL MARKETING:** Brand activations, pop-ups, installations
- **CREATIVE MEDIA:** Film, video, photography, content production
- **INTEGRATED TECHNOLOGY:** AV systems, interactive tech, digital integration

**Each Includes:**
- ANTON headline
- Bebas Neue subheadings
- Share Tech descriptions
- Bold geometric backgrounds
- Duotone project imagery
- Case study links

#### 6. PRODUCTS

**ATLVS Page**
- Platform overview (ANTON heading)
