## üé≠ Design Elements & Components

### Geometric Elements to Include
- Circles, squares, triangles as accent shapes
- Halftone patterns for texture
- Diagonal stripes for energy
- Grid overlays for structure
- Bold arrows and lines for direction
- Abstract compositions as backgrounds
- Pop art explosion shapes
- Ben-Day dots for depth

### Component Specifications

#### Navigation
```
Component: Header/Navigation
- Fixed position with ANTON logo wordmark
- Black background, white text (or inverted)
- Bebas Neue menu items (uppercase)
- Mobile: Hamburger ‚Üí full-screen black overlay
- Desktop: Horizontal with minimal dropdowns
- CTA: "START A PROJECT" (Bebas Neue, outlined)
- Geometric underline on hover
```

#### Footer
```
Component: Footer
- Multi-column on black background
- Bebas Neue column headers (white, uppercase)
- Share Tech links/info (white/grey-400)
- Share Tech Mono copyright/legal (grey-500)
- Newsletter signup (minimal input)
- Bold geometric dividing lines
- Custom B&W geometric social icons
```

#### Cards
```
Component Types:
1. Project Card
   - Duotone image
   - Bebas Neue title
   - Share Tech Mono metadata
   - Thick borders, hard shadows
   - Hover: scale + invert

2. Service Card
   - Geometric icon
   - Bebas Neue heading
   - Share Tech description
   - Outlined or filled style

3. Statistic Card
   - ANTON numbers
   - Bebas Neue label
   - Geometric frame
   - Count-up animation
```

#### Forms
```
Component: Form Elements
- Bold outlined inputs
- Bebas Neue labels
- Share Tech placeholders
- Share Tech error messages
- Geometric success/error icons
- Thick borders (2-3px)
- High contrast focus states (geometric outlines)
- 48px minimum touch targets
```

#### Buttons
```
Component: Button/CTA
- Bebas Neue text (uppercase)
- Two styles:
  1. Outlined (white on black, black on white)
  2. Filled (inverts on hover)
- Geometric arrows or icons
- Minimum 48px height
- Thick borders (2-3px)
- Scale or invert on hover
```

#### Media Components
```
Components:
1. Video Player
   - Custom B&W controls
   - Geometric play/pause buttons
   - Progress bar with thick styling

2. Image Gallery
   - All images duotone/B&W
   - Lightbox: black bg, white UI
   - Geometric navigation arrows
   - Halftone hover overlay

3. Background Video
   - Converted to B&W
   - Lazy loading
   - Geometric placeholder shapes
```

### Animation Specifications
```javascript
// Animation Types to Implement

1. Page Transitions
   - Hard cuts, wipes
   - Geometric reveals
   - No soft fades

2. Scroll-Triggered
   - Fade in
   - Slide up/sideways
   - Scale
   - Rotate
   - Parallax with geometric shapes

3. Hover States
   - Scale (1.0 ‚Üí 1.05)
   - Color invert (black ‚Üî white)
   - Geometric mask reveals
   - Halftone overlay fade

4. Loading States
   - Geometric shape loaders
   - Halftone patterns
   - Progress bars (thick, geometric)

5. Cursor Effects (Desktop, Optional)
   - Follow cursor with geometric shape
   - Size changes on hover
   - B&W only

6. Micro-interactions
   - Button press (scale down)
   - Input focus (thick border)
   - Menu expand (geometric wipe)
   - Tooltip reveal (hard edge)
```

