  width={1920}
  height={1080}
  quality={85}
  priority={true} // for above-fold images
  className="duotone-filter" // apply B&W filter
/>
```

**Image Processing Pipeline:**
1. Convert all uploads to high-contrast B&W
2. Generate multiple sizes (responsive images)
3. Serve WebP/AVIF formats where supported
4. Implement lazy loading for below-fold images
5. Use blur placeholders (geometric shapes)

