## ‚ôø Accessibility Requirements

### WCAG 2.1 AA Compliance

**Checklist:**
- [ ] Keyboard navigation fully functional
- [ ] Screen reader tested (NVDA, JAWS, VoiceOver)
- [ ] Color contrast ratios meet AA standards (easily achieved with B&W)
- [ ] Focus indicators visible (thick geometric outlines)
- [ ] Skip navigation links implemented
- [ ] ARIA labels on interactive elements
- [ ] Form labels properly associated
- [ ] Error messages descriptive and linked
- [ ] Alt text on all images
- [ ] Video captions (if applicable)
- [ ] Reduced motion preferences respected
- [ ] Touch targets minimum 48x48px
- [ ] Semantic HTML structure
- [ ] Heading hierarchy logical

**Reduced Motion Implementation:**
```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  * {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

**Focus Styles:**
```css
/* Visible, geometric focus indicators */
*:focus {
  outline: 3px solid white;
  outline-offset: 4px;
}

/* Dark mode variant */
.dark *:focus {
  outline-color: black;
}
```

